Idea: Created by Khueen with the help of Al'Knoxus the Photonic Archgod and previous Epicenter of Shadow, they're a rare robot who's made of solidified shadows. Having metalic/robotic cores for hearts, it gathers and manipulates shadows to form their bodies. These shadows can touch solid objects, be touched, but does not harm the shadekin if damaged, it merely tires them out more as its core needs to solidify more shadows. It's also mostly immune to frequencies and vibrations, instead being weakened by light.

